    <main class="steel-page snap-page">
      <section class="steel-section intro-section">
        <div class="section-kicker">Buyer FAQ</div>
        <h1>Common questions before ordering stainless steel.</h1>
        <p class="section-lede">Quick answers for stainless steel coil, strip, sheet, surface finish, processing, packaging, and delivery.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="steel-section grid-section">
        <article class="info-panel">
          <span>01</span>
          <h2>What stainless steel grades do you supply?</h2>
          <p>Common cold rolled grades include 201, 304, 304L, 316, 316L, 409, 410 and 430. We can also source mill-order grades through partner steel mills when stock is not available.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="info-panel">
          <span>02</span>
          <h2>What processing services are available?</h2>
          <p>We provide cut-to-length, slitting, brushed finish, mirror polishing, protective film, leveling and customized packaging for coil, strip and sheet orders.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="info-panel">
          <span>03</span>
          <h2>How is stainless steel packed?</h2>
          <p>Material can be packed with moisture protection, wooden pallets, metal edge protection, inner paper, PVC film and export-ready reinforcement according to shipping route and customer handling requirements.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="info-panel">
          <span>04</span>
          <h2>Can you support stable supply?</h2>
          <p>Yes. Ningbo Wanguang operates with China and Cambodia production bases and cooperates with domestic mills to improve lead time reliability and supply-chain stability.</p>
        </article>
      </section>
